            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Meta、亞馬遜、谷歌:摩根士丹利列出第一季財報優先順序",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/C7XPfeVSxETz0.J6_5.vow--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA5I05A_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"摩根士丹利\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:摩根士丹利;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/摩根士丹利\">摩根士丹利</a>在Meta、亞馬遜和谷歌公布第一季業績前,列出了其偏好排序,依序為Meta、亞馬遜和谷歌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Brian Nowak在給客戶的報告中表示,該行\"優先順序為META、AMZN、GOOGL\",並指出將影響2026年前盈利預測修正和股價表現的四大宏觀主題。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利強調\"營收加速和GenAI投資回報率的進一步信號\"是首要主題,指出廣告和超大規模雲端服務營收的持續上升,將影響投資者支付更高估值倍數的意願。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6274d05a-1566-365b-b12b-1cb4a6f98ef4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行還指出2027年資本支出預期上升,稱其對超大規模雲端服務支出的預測\"比市場共識高出約15%\",而投資強度峰值的不確定性可能限制估值。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在消費者方面,摩根士丹利警告\"目前股價尚未反映疲軟跡象\",並指出品牌廣告市場出現早期疲軟跡象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行補充說\"GOOGL股價未反映任何顛覆風險,而META股價未反映MetaAI的任何成功\",使用戶行為轉變成為本季度的關鍵觀察項目。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Meta仍是摩根士丹利的首選。該公司表示,Meta引導更強勁營收增長的能力對於\"展示其GPU/GenAI投資的投資回報率\"至關重要。該行也在關注MetaAI在各應用程式中的推出以及\"Meta報導的裁員計劃的明確性\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於亞馬遜,焦點在於AWS,摩根士丹利預測第一季/2026年增長為\"29%/31%\",並預期利潤率將保持在30%出頭至中段。該行還預測\"2027年GAAP每股盈利達到10至11美元\"的路徑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於谷歌,根據該報告,預計將實現高十位數百分比的付費搜索增長和60%的Google Cloud年增長率,增量利潤率\"上季度達到56%\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/meta-%E4%BA%9E%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%9C-%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C-%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9%E5%88%97%E5%87%BA%E7%AC%AC-%E5%AD%A3%E8%B2%A1%E5%A0%B1%E5%84%AA%E5%85%88%E9%A0%86%E5%BA%8F-143645530.html",
